When I was 8 my parents got me Lago blocks for Christmas and I had some other cars and trucks. I also got a Highway Patrol/Police Uniform for kids from Sears for Christmas. I would play more with my uniform and the Lagos. I could make many things with them, cars, trucks, houses, even a small town so I could use my other cars and trucks in. I was also into Star Trek and I had models and played with them as well. I was an only child and I kep my bed room clean, but had a play room for when the weather was bad and played outside when I lived in the country on a farm or even in a town. Thoes was the days.
